              <div class="tab-pane fade cmu-pkg-details   active show " id="cmu-tab-104048-1" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="cmu-tab-104048-1-tab" style=color:#015BBC;background-color:#FCFDC3>
                    <div class="tab-pane-content"><p>The UNCC virtual meeting package helps identify your specific needs to ensure the production of a successful virtual event. Let your delegates connect, network, and participate in interactive sessions with our custom virtual event services designed to deliver highly interactive events that will delight your participants.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Our virtual meeting package allows you to broadcast globally to your participants and connects you with the world from a single location. Our services start from online registration, onboard&nbsp;speakers,&nbsp;and participants, manage live events, to generate reports and data. Our conference technology team is willing to support you with their technical expertise to help you deliver a solid performance.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/uncc/meeting-packages"><u>Read more</u></a></p>
</div>
                  </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade cmu-pkg-details  " id="cmu-tab-104048-2" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="cmu-tab-104048-2-tab" style=color:#015BBC;background-color:#DDFBDA>
                    <div class="tab-pane-content"><p>The UNCC offers a tailor-made hybrid meeting package for the best of both on-site and online participants. Our logistic team and conference technology team are high tech, low touch, and hygiene driven. While core organiser and participants are on-site, you can easily reach your online speakers and participants through a digital presence.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Our hybrid meeting package allows your delegates to participate remotely from wherever they are in the world with their own languages through our Conference Management and Simultaneous Interpretation (CMSI) System. We offer various types of virtual platforms of your choice. Any event organiser can benefit from this meeting package and so can your meeting participants.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/uncc/meeting-packages"><u>Read more</u></a></p>
</div>
                  </div>
              <div class="tab-pane fade cmu-pkg-details  " id="cmu-tab-104048-3" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="cmu-tab-104048-3-tab" style=color:#015BBC;background-color:#DDF2FD>
                    <div class="tab-pane-content"><p>UNCC offers&nbsp;an excellent meetings and events venue with&nbsp;five&nbsp;conference rooms with built-in&nbsp;Conference Management and Simultaneous Interpretation (CMSI) System,&nbsp;interpretation booths and audio/visual system and&nbsp;nine&nbsp;multi-functional small and medium-size meeting rooms and a theatre.&nbsp;Additionally, we&nbsp;have the secretariat office suites for&nbsp;organisers, delegates’ lounges and working area for delegates/participants with free high-speed Wi-Fi throughout the building, and the Reception Hall for multi-purpose events and social functions with on-site catering services.&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><a href="/uncc/meeting-packages"><u>Read more</u></a></p>
